raph","paragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"[Danvers, Massachusetts, Jan 26th, 2021] MAXAM is proud to announce the next generation of the MAXAM Tire app.  In continual efforts to improve customer experience, the optimized app has been developed to provide the industry with a revolutionary experience no matter where you are in the world.","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"[Danvers, Massachusetts, Jan 26th, 2021] MAXAM is proud to announce the next generation of the MAXAM Tire app.  In continual efforts to improve customer experience, the optimized app has been developed to provide the industry with a revolutionary experience no matter where you are in the world.","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8112-ad03-ec5800e401ce","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-81d5-9bef-cb7d9258fc12"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T21:59:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T21:59:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"paragraph","paragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"The optimized version MAXAM app was designed to be an easily accessible hub of information for users on the go. With updated features such as our product library, all the information you need on MAXAM products is available at your fingertips.  “Our goal remains to be the best Business Solutions Provider in the industry. By releasing this next generation of our app, we can continue to provide our customers the advancement they need from our team, no matter their location,” says Troy Kline, President of MAXAM Tire North America, Inc.","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"The optimized version MAXAM app was designed to be an easily accessible hub of information for users on the go. With updated features such as our product library, all the information you need on MAXAM products is available at your fingertips.  “Our goal remains to be the best Business Solutions Provider in the industry. By releasing this next generation of our app, we can continue to provide our customers the advancement they need from our team, no matter their location,” says Troy Kline, President of MAXAM Tire North America, Inc.","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-81f6-acfb-f13f4e3bacdb","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-81d5-9bef-cb7d9258fc12"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T21:59:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T21:59:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"paragraph","paragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"Available for both iOS and Android, the newly updated and optimized MAXAM app features more tools than ever along with an easy to navigate menu. Users now have access to both the TKPH/TMPH calculator for off-the-road applications and the all-new agricultural air pressure calculator along with these additional features:","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"Available for both iOS and Android, the newly updated and optimized MAXAM app features more tools than ever along with an easy to navigate menu. Users now have access to both the TKPH/TMPH calculator for off-the-road applications and the all-new agricultural air pressure calculator along with these additional features:","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"objec